      <title>国际货币基金组织就财政赤字发出警告，塞内加尔债券价格下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/senegal-bonds-drop-as-imf-flags-fiscal-deficit-election-may-delay-next-review</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际货币基金组织表示，预计塞内加尔的财政状况将会恶化，随后该国美元债券价格下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/senegal-bonds-drop-as-imf-flags-fiscal-deficit-election-may-delay-next-review</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 15:19:12 GMT</pubDate>
